title: Monthly change of the profile creation NFT
body:
monthly change of the profile creation NFT

I believe that monthly there should be a change in the first profile NFT when we pay 1.5 cake. for the reason of limiting and always creating the possibility of nft being valued for its level of difficulty.

the proposal is that every month the profile start NFT is changed by others.



this will enhance the profile nfts already created over time due to lack and difficulty in the long run and creating an overall valuation in all nfts of initiation.
